|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT REMOTE      |             |80      |1820        |
|2 |  └─TOP-N SORT             |             |80      |1750        |
|3 |    └─HASH GROUP BY        |             |80      |1736        |
|4 |      └─HASH JOIN          |             |88      |1704        |
|5 |        ├─HASH JOIN        |             |88      |588         |
|6 |        │ ├─TABLE FULL SCAN|reason       |2       |5           |
|7 |        │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN|store_returns|3000    |333         |
|8 |        └─TABLE FULL SCAN  |store_sales  |5000    |637         |
====================================================================
